Analysis Based On Both Horoscopes

Star Analysis For Abhishek Bachchan and Aishwarya Rai

The birth star of Aishwarya Rai is Purva Ashadha. The epitome of charm, beauty, and grace is ruled by the planet of beauty and luxury, Venus. This will make the woman very much attractive and diplomatic. On the other hand, he is ruled by the planet of stability and discipline, Saturn. Venus empowered woman and Saturn empower man will have a lot of understanding towards each other. This gives strong and sufficient compatibilities. However, being born in the birth star ruled by Saturn, he must make efforts to make her feel attached. The romantic and outgoing lady may feel detached due to the silent nature of the man. Regardless of this aspect, the couple has a great understanding and amicable with each other.
